Automatic partitioning
<i>"$I18N_fdistTypeautomatic"</i> deletes all data from the client hard disk. m23 will create two new partitions, one for the data and base system and one for swapping.

<U>Step by step:</U>
<ol>
<LI>Select <i>"$I18N_fdistTypeautomatic"</i>.</LI>
<LI>Click on the <i>"$I18N_refresh"</i> button to see the suggested partitioning.</LI>
<LI>Click on <i>"$I18N_format_client"</i> to accept changes.</LI>
</ol>
